Ticket Number: 00423637
Ticket Subject: 11078 Network Printers and no other Devices shown in Device Control
Ticket Details: On the Device Control Tab we have currently 11078 almost identical network printers and it shows no other devices. We do not have that amount of network printers. When searched for a specific device like devicetype "bluetooth" it correctly lists all available bluetooth devices.
Since there are so many identical network printers we have no real overlook over the devices. Also the appliance is still on Ubuntu 14.04.5 LTS. How can we upgrade the server?

Thank you!
